    <!-- Leader Dialog -->
    <Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_FIRST_MEET_LEADER_FURINA_ANY" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Why are you just standing there with your mouth gaping? Ah, you must be stunned and at a loss for words... Understandable, it is I after all... Fontaine's most beloved star, Furina. I'm on a very tight schedule, so you're lucky to even get an appointment with me.</Text>
